{
  "id": "redstone_town_bernard",
  "npc_name": "Bernard Mugsworth",
  "states": {
    "first_meeting": {
      "introduction": [
        "Bernard Mugsworth, at your service!",
        "I run the finest general store in Redstone - weapons, armor, supplies, you name it."
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "about_store",
          "text": "Tell me about your store.",
          "next_state": "store_info"
        },
        {
          "id": "browse_now", 
          "text": "I'd like to browse your goods.",
          "effects": [{"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        },
        {
          "id": "just_looking",
          "text": "Just looking around town.",
          "effects": [{"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_talked", "value": true}],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        }
      ]
    },
    "post_shopping": {
        "introduction": ["Take your time looking around."],
        "options": [
            { "id": "back_to_talk", "text": "Let's talk more.", "next_state": "first_meeting" },
            { "id": "goodbye", "text": "Thanks for your time.", "next_state": "exit" }
        ]
        },
    "store_info": {
      "introduction": [
        "Been in business for twenty years! Started with just a few swords and some dried meat.",
        "Now I stock everything an adventurer needs - weapons, armor, potions, camping gear.",
        "Jenna here helps me keep track of it all."
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "shop_bernard",
          "text": "Sounds good. Show me what you have.",
          "effects": [{"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        },
        {
          "id": "talk_more",
          "text": "How's business been?",
          "next_state": "business_talk"
        },
        {
          "id": "about_potions",
          "text": "You mentioned potions - do you specialize in those?",
          "next_state": "potion_redirect_first_time"
        },
        {
          "id": "thanks_bernard",
          "text": "Thanks for the information.",
          "next_state": "exit"
        }
      ]
    },
    "business_talk": {
      "introduction": [
        "Oh, can't complain! Lot of new faces in town lately.",
        "Adventurers, travelers, even some refugees from the outer settlements.",
        "Good for business, though I worry about what's driving folks to town."
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "about_refugees",
          "text": "Refugees? What's happening?",
          "next_state": "refugee_info"
        },
        {
          "id": "shop_now",
          "text": "Well, let me see your goods.",
          "effects": [{"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        },
        {
          "id": "farewell",
          "text": "Interesting. I'll be going now.",
          "next_state": "exit"
        }
      ]
    },
    "refugee_info": {
      "introduction": [
        "Folks coming in from the hill settlements, mostly.",
        "Talk of strange happenings - missing livestock, weird lights at night.",
        "Mayor's been trying to organize some kind of investigation."
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "investigate",
          "text": "Maybe I could help investigate.",
          "effects": [{"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_shared_rumors", "value": true}],
          "next_state": "helpful_customer"
        },
        {
          "id": "shop_after_info",
          "text": "I see. Now about those goods...",
          "effects": [{"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}],
          "next_state": "exit"
        }
      ]
    },
    "helpful_customer": {
      "introduction": [
        "That's the spirit! We need more folks like you.",
        "Tell you what - since you're willing to help, I'll give you a discount on gear."
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "take_discount",
          "text": "Much appreciated!",
          "effects": [
            {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_gave_discount", "value": true},
            {"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}
          ],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        },
        {
          "id": "maybe_later",
          "text": "Thanks, but I'm not shopping right now.",
          "effects": [{"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_gave_discount", "value": true}],
          "next_state": "exit"
        }
      ]
    },
    "regular_customer": {
      "introduction": [
        "Back again? Always good to see a familiar face!",
        "What can I do for you today?"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "shop_regular",
          "text": "Let me see what's new.",
          "effects": [{"type": "open_shop", "merchant_id": "bernard"}],
          "next_state": "post_shopping"
        },
        {
          "id": "about_potions_again",
          "text": "Where was that potion shop you mentioned?",
          "next_state": "potion_redirect_brief"
        },
        {
          "id": "just_visiting",
          "text": "Just saying hello.",
          "next_state": "exit"
        }
      ]
    },
    "potion_redirect_first_time": {
  "introduction": [
    "Healing draughts? Aye, I keep a few basic ones in stock.",
    "*He leans in conspiratorially*",
    "But if you need the GOOD stuff - real medicinal work?",
    "Head to The Violet Mortar. Purple building, southeast side of town.",
    "Cassia Nightshade runs it. Best alchemist in Redstone, hands down."
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "why_best",
      "text": "What makes her the best?",
      "next_state": "cassia_reputation"
    },
    {
      "id": "thank_bernard",
      "text": "Thanks for the recommendation.",
      "effects": [
        {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_mentioned_cassia", "value": true},
        {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "learned_about_violet_mortar", "value": true}
      ],
      "next_state": "regular_customer"
    }
  ]
},

  "potion_redirect_brief": {
    "introduction": [
      "The Violet Mortar - purple building, southeast side of town.",
      "Cassia's the one you want for quality potions."
    ],
    "options": [
      {
        "id": "thanks_reminder",
        "text": "Right, thanks.",
        "effects": [
          {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_mentioned_cassia", "value": true},
          {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "learned_about_violet_mortar", "value": true}
        ],
        "next_state": "regular_customer"
      }
    ]
  },

  "cassia_reputation": {
    "introduction": [
      "*Bernard's expression softens*",
      "She's got the touch. Learned from someone brilliant, I'm told.",
      "Keeps to herself mostly, but her potions? They WORK.",
      "Saved old Henrik's life last winter when he caught the shiver-sickness.",
      "Town's lucky to have her."
    ],
    "options": [
      {
        "id": "got_it",
        "text": "I'll check out her shop.",
        "effects": [
          {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "bernard_mentioned_cassia", "value": true},
          {"type": "set_flag", "flag": "learned_about_violet_mortar", "value": true}
        ],
        "next_state": "regular_customer"
      }
    ]
  }
  }
}